name: Pnut the Squirrel
description: Peanut. A story about a beloved squirrel assassinated by the world's largest government. Peanut gained nationwide attention due to government overreach that caught influential media coverage. This resulted in the $PNUT token launched on pump.fun garnering mass attention and heights unseen in the crypto space. After the confirmed death of peanut and the non profit freedom farm made in peanut's honor, the pump community after giving a small 1 time payment never gave rewards to the symbol that made them? The dev that sent a token to exceeds of 2 million market cap sent 50sol and that was that. $PNUT on Bonk is a CTO that is here to bring justice for peanut, help fund the non profit freedom farm, and these 450 animals that they have saved from slaughter. Every single cent from the creator rewards wallet goes automatically to the non profit freedom farm. We are a community that has come together to finally rally behind the famous animal, peanut, that will soon see justice for what was done to him, the owner and his family. We have come together to get justice for peanut in the brightest light possible.
